Development:
* Write controller for lock/password protected screen on iOS. (syzdek)
* Add to BKSplitViewController the ability to toggle the use of the popover
  controller in either portrait or landscape orientations rather than assume
  that only the standard UISplitViewController behavior is desired. (syzdek)
* Add rounded corners to the detail view and master view in a
  BKSplitViewController when displaying both views without a divider view
  seperating the two views. (syzdek)

Bugs:
   BKSplitViewController:
   * When rotating from an orientation with the popover controller to an
     orientation with the master view displayed and the viewOrderReversed had
     been updated since the last orientation transition, the master view does
     not cleanly transition into the window. (syzdek)
   * When toggling bothViewsDisplayed to false when both the master view and
     detail view are displayed, the subviews in the detail view jump to the left
     of the detail view before beginning the animation. (syzdek).
   * Fix handling of -(void)didReceiveMemoryWarning; (syzdek)
